          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>MOJ-certified translation</li>
            <li>Business Bay delivery</li>
            <li>Digital and physical copies</li>
            <li>WhatsApp updates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card pricing-card--featured">
          <h3>Express</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">From AED 300</div>
          <p class="pricing-time">6-hour delivery</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Everything in Standard</li>
            <li>Priority queue</li>
            <li>Same-day completion</li>
            <li>Court deadline support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>VIP Concierge</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">From AED 500</div>
          <p class="pricing-time">1-hour draft</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Everything in Express</li>
            <li>Immediate assignment</li>
            <li>Draft within 60 minutes</li>
            <li>Dedicated coordinator</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Getting Started</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <p>Send your documents via WhatsApp from your Business Bay office. Contracts, governance documents, employment letters—whatever needs translation. We will confirm approach, timeline, and cost promptly.</p>
        
        <p>For litigation support or due diligence with multiple documents, we can discuss volume arrangements and coordinated delivery. For corporate accounts, ask about our ongoing relationship terms.</p>
        
        <p>Digital PDFs are delivered immediately upon completion. Physical copies with MOJ stamp can be at your Business Bay tower the same day for Express service, or next business day for Standard.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

